main event: A UFO sighting was reported on February 9, 1957, in Lake Worth, Florida, involving one object observed for 22 minutes.
interesting points: The sighting lasted for 22 minutes,The object was observed visually through binoculars,The observer concluded the sighting was a child's fluorescent box kite,The report came from Project 10073 of the USAF,The sighting was categorized as an aerial-visual observation.
sighted object: one object, described as a box kite
